query:
WITH update_info as (
            SELECT protected
            FROM tabular
            WHERE warehouse_id = $1 AND tabular_id = $2
        ), update as (
            UPDATE tabular
            SET deleted_at = $3
            WHERE warehouse_id = $1 AND tabular_id = $2
                AND ((NOT protected) OR $4)
            RETURNING warehouse_id, tabular_id
        )
        SELECT protected as "protected!", (SELECT tabular_id from update) from update_info
